text: Melun Villaroche Aerodrome () is an aerodrome north of Melun. Melun is a commune in the Seine-et-Marne department in the Île-de-France region in north- central France. The airport is east-southeast of Moissy-Cramayel and southeast of Paris. A campus of the École nationale de l'aviation civile (French civil aviation university) is also in the aerodrome.Melun ==References== Category:Airports in France Category:Seine-et-Marne
